_sText:
About 90% of this map is made of custom textures/sprites i  made in Paint. That other 10% is water(From snow level.), skybox, Glass, and the Black and White textures hammer already has.

I named the map cartoony because i pretty much drew everything in the map. This map is not easy at all. I made it for more advanced b-hoppers. It's only about 4 levels long. There's one secret in this map try to find it! :) 

I hope you enjoy!


-distoRted
